We made it to the FORBES list my dearest Jovians! 

Remember the days when I called you that ? That’s how long I’ve been here in this space 😂
I’ve seen a lot of awards come and go during my time as a digital creator. Nothing has felt this rewarding, nothing has made me feel this full of gratitude as much as being on the Top 100 lost by @forbesindia 

They have researched genuine reach and I couldn’t have asked for more. Thank you so much @forbesindia ❤️❤️

And, Thank YOU my loves, for being there for me. We have come a long way, you and I. Thank you for being my support and strength. I truly truly appreciate you and am grateful to you! 

I was actually quite disappointed in myself this year for not being able to be as consistent as I hoped for due to my brand launch. But hey, that happened too! And here we are on the Forbes list too.

Mathi, now let me go have my chicken curry and pathiri, vayar  niranju 🥹
